Title: Cisco IP WebDialerControl
Description:
This control Will let you connect you ASP webSite to you Cisco IP Phone using the Cisco WebDialer 
With a few setting in both you can make calls from with one click  with out enter the phone number 
Must be next to your Cisco phone 
You are still using it this will just dial
